                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4 fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
                <div class="team-card">
                    <div class="team-avatar">
                        👩‍🏢
                    </div>
                    <h5 class="mb-2">Nguyễn Hoàng Thiên Ân</h5>
